  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"traditional\"><h2 id=\"cMFfO\"><span class=\"ne-text\">插入日历</span></h2><p id=\"bdf09171af47708dc299e2616145e6e0\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">用户可通过工具栏上的“插入卡片”按钮或者 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 快捷方式来插入日历，分别如下图所示：</span></p><p id=\"b1e078493d26d4206057ff44dbfee65d\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"sGyRJ\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过工具栏插入</span></h3><p id=\"1b203fd610776bd71c08246ecb2ea582\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634181587261-1c08e5c5-a977-4dfd-bcf0-54b51ea5e1fd.png\" width=\"201.33333333333334\" id=\"u9f2b6a77\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"0b4d7c412ed58c68fed3be3ea0b90c14\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"GIQJM\"></h3><h3 id=\"x6Mox\"><span class=\"ne-text\">快捷方式插入</span></h3><p id=\"90aea4aacf24fba5901ca93a7fa6b183\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"8a59ba2db25de0968e0496a8d5dbe8ea\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">输入 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 激活卡片快捷插入，通过日历卡片的中文、拼音、英文可快速搜索到日历卡片进行插入。</span></p><p id=\"e0746c8885a0bcca525133173f4fe831\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634181604468-09fef372-5c02-481b-bdf0-5d0d3cfd73dd.png\" width=\"568.6666666666666\" id=\"u285a9369\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"bfa11b02db6ca0f02beb497e8e01c812\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"539125c0514fd9ffbffadaa594483183\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"B7pDC\"><span class=\"ne-text\">新建日程</span></h2><p id=\"ff38eb7d84376fe7c3a771e780820540\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">新插入的日历如下图所示，其中，蓝色背景的日期表示“今天”：</span></p><p id=\"7723d81256c7ef603588551f17af0af4\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591077593951-0994f44f-4feb-4410-9af8-b27940d832cd.png\" width=\"820\" id=\"fD0sZ\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"f6fd121b907e33baed4cda51d64d9c1f\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">用户可以通过单击（或双击）对应日期的单元格创建一个日程，如下图所示：</span></p><p id=\"549cccc122a9d086aeb1accca507ca82\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591077773678-2f06948f-3404-4d0a-9551-bbc5aa335a3b.png\" width=\"811\" id=\"PDNcp\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"7fcc1decd7428393bec88eec53c45f18\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">编辑日程标题、起止日期和说明后，单击日程详情面板区域外的任意位置，可保存该日程，效果如下：</span></p><p id=\"f18e8f2426edc05886eb5f73a205c126\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591077928999-7c752a58-77ab-4e8e-a2e8-684c70cd7c67.png\" width=\"802\" id=\"aGLIf\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"78fcf49c89a4898b050fdc2928dd0c28\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"BWmzk\"></h2><h2 id=\"KsFex\"><span class=\"ne-text\">编辑日程</span></h2><p id=\"2b97a899c270993b4bb230f4aed4b2db\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">你可以通过以下方式，重新打开日程的编辑面板，以进行日程的调整：</span></p><p id=\"821b49c57dfef811a876c80cbf3b18fd\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"1c7d6159e69c0268116b367cb4de4c05\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击要修改的日程，此时，颜色会</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">变深</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，表示已选中；<br /></span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591078045866-4d16646c-c020-42f4-a069-01153b3da804.png\" width=\"797\" id=\"beN0L\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></li><li id=\"eb52c9d923c73471b9ae290e5292764e\"><span class=\"ne-text\">再次单击日程，会弹出编辑面板，此时可对日程进行修改。<br /></span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591078067620-0ab25a63-c4aa-48be-ac10-0b3f5a65441a.png\" width=\"830\" id=\"hN2Vu\" class=\"ne-image\"></li></ol><p id=\"758f2ff2f153784252e28e91e8e886aa\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"c07f24593b33fb39a00063277e9149d1\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">此外，你也可以</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">直接双击</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">要修改的日程即可打开日程详情编辑面板。</span></p><p id=\"d08ef728040a06eec9fca0c1344d7e0c\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"EmSs0\"></h3><h3 id=\"txdG7\"></h3><h3 id=\"QZkxs\"><span class=\"ne-text\">修改日期</span></h3><p id=\"7cc9acb7f674855d0cd0f70386e21079\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h4 id=\"HApaD\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在详情面板中修改日期</span></h4><p id=\"a7c4e7c4f5f0228c1bce51786049a852\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">双击打开日程详情面板，点击面板中的日期，会打开日期选择面板，可通过操作该面板完成起止日期的修改，如下图所示：</span></p><p id=\"264e93bae952b8c49ad93a8f943986d4\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591078282680-a62c7c96-21ac-4f70-9da6-7f7f576c1a9d.png\" width=\"663\" id=\"fbAPB\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"bf663710d00a338408bcf7975e512d1e\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h4 id=\"lu6XJ\"><span class=\"ne-text\">拖拽日程修改日期</span></h4><p id=\"3ccc84b6526ffc700f4ffe7d94c1d4a0\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">你也可以直接通过拖拽日程的方式修改起止日期。</span></p><p id=\"e8832d7210d23954a1e981ee785338e9\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ecd823a9f3c8f3fd747378ab62269670\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">修改起始日期</span></strong></p><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"26887f08cf1b9f9dd0c980992b26609c\"><span class=\"ne-text\">单击选中要调整日期的日程，此时日程背景色会变成深色；</span></li><li id=\"2b737d87e266a369785e396424b47053\"><span class=\"ne-text\">按住鼠标，然后拖动该日程到目标日期对应的单元格即可（移动过程中，会以绿色边框高亮显示目标单元格）。<br /></span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591078569451-a430b93f-10c8-4f36-bc68-79ed60354435.png\" width=\"852\" id=\"ZPxGR\" class=\"ne-image\"></li></ol><p id=\"c93bdbbfd716cd2697a4ab61f2693b48\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"e8204e50a27f71dd6a80f3dd4e41bfc3\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">修改结束日期</span></strong></p><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"fb4f5362bbb65ec7f4557fa11d15ba85\"><span class=\"ne-text\">单击选中要调整日期的日程，此时日程背景色会变成深色；</span></li><li id=\"8d065e3eef7a5ac0cd81b19f5e3a2b82\"><span class=\"ne-text\">鼠标移动到日程的</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">尾部</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，此时，鼠标指针会变成一个“左右移动箭头”的形状；</span></li><li id=\"6d73333ac5818b62cac92314517fd87e\"><span class=\"ne-text\">按下鼠标，然后移动鼠标到期望的结束日期，释放鼠标即可完成对结束日期的调整。（移动过程中，会以绿色边框高亮调整后的日程所跨越的日期）。<br /></span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591078813236-422d9106-3fdf-49be-8f77-8576b2deb3d6.png\" width=\"928\" id=\"WUICK\" class=\"ne-image\"></li></ol><p id=\"258d899706159f89199b125be6320580\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"fa9dad8a54397c81e770eaae69c6869b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><h3 id=\"ri7m6\"><span class=\"ne-text\">添加链接</span></h3><div class=\"ne-quote\"><p id=\"ec3b7f256037d3ab4409fc2ec9041e3b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">注意：编辑态下，日程详情中的链接显示为文本，也不可点击跳转。</span></p></div><p id=\"98360378d5fb8ae5d317610aa6ca80b2\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"da63ae7a184f52b79dac0a22a281d544\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在编辑态下，用户可以输入一个 http（或 https ）协议的链接，该链接在阅读态下，会自动识别为链接样式，点击后跳转到目标网站。如下图所示：</span></p><p id=\"4f29ed7b151e2658ef0cb798388e2d92\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"99ea4ce56d60e6d8d89fbd1090825580\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">编辑态</span></strong></p><p id=\"b0d379cff4e85716661c66e05ea18530\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591082356793-ea3dd3ae-6e66-41d3-a7e0-6ca84711875d.png\" width=\"1308\" id=\"CMqsq\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"88e7600d7a6303cbf28a09cc7897e62b\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"b0c7e547b03e8c9efa9d0883e3530edb\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">阅读态</span></strong></p><p id=\"dbc4b8ec05a6d9bbb41205deff287542\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591079117520-9a967e9d-e936-44d1-8fdb-9bde0c55c6bd.png\" width=\"1073\" id=\"jkqz9\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"78db45882d41e7ce90d35c8c57996b53\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"355540225bc3d2f5f8353095ca5d2d5a\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ecf0b58102f9c1b7823cffd78c27ad5d\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"44ce61d3c397d8a3f38f29eab3225fa2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><h2 id=\"ggCrc\"><span class=\"ne-text\">删除日程</span></h2><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"ef20409b9d59d1a7f102d667fbca837c\"><span class=\"ne-text\">鼠标单击要删除的日程，此时该日程背景色会变深；</span></li><li id=\"3a0f6f899971f7090a2da314eb22305c\"><span class=\"ne-text\">按下键盘上的 delete 键（或 backspace 键），即可删除该日程。</span></li></ol><p id=\"b53754686e8685ff49412f0a31fa9bc5\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"97c192573b182cd59ec380d2f48ada71\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"Uz6FI\"><span class=\"ne-text\">查看日历</span></h2><p id=\"273c01fb1c2498fc85e9e0ddeefe2017\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"966054a0b56167520803238bfce4d7f5\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">当文档发布后，日历卡片展示如下：</span></p><p id=\"59d8edd1fe8ffa1a6ae42c1f2fa817a4\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591079160338-e959570f-c943-4c85-9991-bed60067b67a.png\" width=\"857\" id=\"RmWH7\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"18774e6b2824d308f4fea85fd162e8d8\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"477c46ff501c5e6e1fcc97443086db03\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">用户可以点击具体的日程，即可查看日程详情：</span></p><p id=\"u68cd1176\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591079193638-3281f48e-a5a8-4a17-af95-f6531c9de5e8.png\" width=\"1254\" id=\"U7fzs\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"531777eb1314c91cae03e6fcebab409b\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u24d236ae\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ub4c263f5\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(23, 26, 29)\">如果对语雀有任何的建议或意见，可以提交反馈：</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀反馈通道</span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">， 感谢你的支持！</span></p></div>",
  "slug": 13900847,
  "title": "如何插入日历"
}